  "general_provisions": "This bill requires the posting of certain information relating to a candidate for public office.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>requires an election officer to post the following information relating to a candidate for public office:<hr><ltbullet1>the name and campaign contact information of the candidate;<hr><ltbullet1>the office that the candidate is seeking; and<hr><ltbullet1>the political party affiliation of the candidate, regardless of whether the candidate is a candidate for partisan or nonpartisan office; and<hr><ltbullet>exempts a judge who is a candidate in a retention election from the provisions of this bill. ",
